          <div class="p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-900/20 to-teal-900/20 rounded-lg border border-green-500/30">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Matrix Space (Coming Soon)</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 text-slate-300">Our decentralized Matrix space for structured discussions and technical collaboration.</p>
            <MatrixInvite />
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-400">New to Matrix? <a href="https://matrix.org/docs/guides/introduction" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-green-400 hover:underline">Learn more here.</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Upcoming Events</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-100">Stay tuned for announcements about governance meetings, developer calls, AMAs (Ask Me Anything sessions), and community workshops.</p>
          {/* Placeholder for events list or calendar embed */}
          <div class="bg-slate-800/70 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-600">
