      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center">Community Resources</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-800/70 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-600">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-white">Forum / GitHub Discussions</h3>
            <p class="text-sm mb-3 text-gray-100">For longer-form discussions, proposals, and asynchronous collaboration. <a href="https://github.com/orgs/InterCooperative-Network/discussions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-400 hover:underline">(Link to GitHub Discussions)</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/70 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-600">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-white">Documentation Hub</h3>
            <p class="text-sm mb-3 text-gray-100">Our comprehensive guides, tutorials, and technical references. <a href="https://docs.intercooperative.network" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sky-400 hover:underline">Visit Docs</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/70 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-600">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-white">Contribution Guide</h3>
            <p class="text-sm mb-3 text-gray-100">Learn how to contribute to ICN projects, from code to documentation. <a href="/contribute" class="text-sky-400 hover:underline">(Link to /contribute page - to be created)</a></p> 
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <aside class="bg-slate-800/90 border border-slate-600 p-8 my-12 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Get Involved!</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-100">Whether you're a developer, designer, writer, or just passionate about a cooperative internet, there's a place for you in ICN. Join our Discord, explore projects, or start a discussion.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="https://discord.gg/GCWKPWdvgH" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">
        Join Discord Server
      </a>
      <span class="btn btn-secondary cursor-not-allowed opacity-50">Matrix server coming soon</span>
    </div>
  </aside>

